{"tid":2400540,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"d2黃色市集有人報狗","createTime":"2021-02-09T04:45:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-09T12:58:27.000Z","uid":305297,"like":34,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"d8f287fbed6dde8e404bf2411bed70e8f887d026","tid":2400540,"uid":305297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T04:45:39.000Z","msg":"尋日見到有d2天台檔主突然話取消市集 咁我就好奇發生咩事<br />\nJer仔<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iB5jJOj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiB5jJOj.png&h=2010802b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFHproduction <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NpjAg8s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNpjAg8s.png&h=495bcbc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來係尋日太大風有檔口被吹走+有貨物損毁 <br />\n成班店主就嬲主辦單位（白紙市集）人手安排+防風措施不足（沙包不足）最後好似傾唔掂數<br />\nJer仔ig live<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/tv/CLCj_RGDyTg/?igshid=9rh0cblyibcq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ftv%2FCLCj_RGDyTg%2F%3Figshid%3D9rh0cblyibcq&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMJmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=9e671fa9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/tv/CLCj_RGDyTg/?igshid=9rh0cblyibcq</a><br />\n<br />\n期間有檔主報狗<br />\nPilotshop<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CLDFKQbgu7j/?igshid=1ijm1np3gyuwf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCLDFKQbgu7j%2F%3Figshid%3D1ijm1np3gyuwf&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMJmCY7kjLy3g2NNjbjbrEl8%3D&h=0ca3d4e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCLDFKQbgu7j%2F%3Figshid%3D1ijm1np3gyuwf&h=837d273c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CLDFKQbgu7j/?igshid=1ijm1np3gyuwf</a><br />\n檔主解釋：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CxnBL3q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCxnBL3q.png&h=498b540a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後白紙市集宣布天台年宵取消+全數退回租金<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AZM3q22.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAZM3q22.png&h=06a032e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實揀得天台預咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />只可以話唔好彩 但為少少利益報狗又係咪真係正確選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83b1d4d3105c1f8edb3e8309800786c18d3227a3","tid":2400540,"uid":305297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T04:48:36.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"aa59e75b92cc7efa4af113393b4ceeae50cc8790","tid":2400540,"uid":305297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T04:51:06.000Z","msg":"自推2/10"},{"pid":"96774abce61d2bacde1541f83b3d5bf1105c12db","tid":2400540,"uid":305297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T04:52:27.000Z","msg":"自推3/10"},{"pid":"3ee8d56598adfe82567b7bf780af6a88ce17bc32","tid":2400540,"uid":305297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T04:53:22.000Z","msg":"自推4/10"},{"pid":"a23b8cdef3229f4fdf0bf504c84426b05948b1ce","tid":2400540,"uid":308760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T04:53:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3e34aee3526b95ff93fe39c38973c6be969eecca","tid":2400540,"uid":305297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T04:54:20.000Z","msg":"自推5/10"},{"pid":"8f28a2a971e9071c6271ff03f0df4002610ff941","tid":2400540,"uid":221571,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T04:54:35.000Z","msg":"唔講報狗<br />\n自己檔野唔睇好啲貨由得啲貨吹走都入人地數？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc6451ad3fea412ee707dea8f87ba6eb1c9f6316","tid":2400540,"uid":6845,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T04:55:09.000Z","msg":"個檔主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aa2